
#1 (high)
	BM_DIRECTORIES_BLACKLIST: list
	This will contain all the directories to exclude when generating archives.

#2 (high)
	BM_DUMP_SYMLINKS: boolean
	Tell if bm has to dump symlinks when generating archives.

#3 (high)
	Never backup the BM_ARCHIVE_REPOSITORY

#4 (low)
	BM_BURNING_KEEP_ISO: boolean
	Tell if we have to make the iso image on disk instead of using a pipe.
	This way, we have to put it somewhere user can find it.

#5 (medium)
	Handle the cron frequency in debocnf.


